data.description: Priced to sell! Looking for a bigger house in the country without the price tag?! Check out this house that is just a few minutes from town but the luxury of the quiet country living and sets on 2.4 acres with a pole barn! This home has 4bd 2ba, over 2600 sq ft and has lots of potential. There is a storm shelter inside the garage as my well as outside.The owners have brand new flooring in several rooms of the house. Get this one before it’s gone.
